<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='154:180'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-1a' );" name="005-1a" class="pb">[005-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='180:188'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='188:196'>　詩總聞卷五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='196:216'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　王質　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:221'>　齊風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='221:227'>　　雞鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='227:234'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='234:252'>雞既鳴矣朝既盈矣匪雞則鳴蒼蠅之聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='252:271'>　非雞鳴乃蠅聲非東眀乃月光所以不安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='271:297'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-1b' );" name="005-1b" class="pb">[005-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='297:304'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='304:323'>東方明矣朝既昌矣匪東方則明月出之光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='323:330'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='330:350'>蟲飛薨薨甘與子同夢㑹且歸矣無庶予子憎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='350:373'>　雖曉尚以同夢為美俾趨朝者且歸令人無多以我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='373:396'>　爾為憎予斥已也子斥君也言不使其歸則二人皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='396:409'>　受多慊也此皆婦人之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='409:432'>　　聞音曰明謨郎切惟皇矣其德克眀如今音餘皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='432:458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-2a' );" name="005-2a" class="pb">[005-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='458:482'>　　　謨郎故詩韻亦不可盡拘古而廢今也夢莫滕切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='482:505'>總聞曰可見賢妃警戒之意孔氏以為非雞實鳴乃蠅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='505:528'>之聲夫人在君所心常警懼故以蠅聲為雞鳴盖謂警</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='528:549'>懼之心亂其神故雞蠅之聲亂其聴也識者更詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='549:554'>　　還</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='554:561'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='561:584'>子之還兮遭我乎峱之間兮並驅從兩肩兮揖我謂我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='584:588'>儇兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='588:614'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-2b' );" name="005-2b" class="pb">[005-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='614:621'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='621:644'>子之茂兮遭我乎峱之道兮並驅從兩牡兮揖我謂我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='644:648'>好兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='648:655'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='655:678'>子之昌兮遭我乎峱之陽兮並驅從兩狼兮揖我謂我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='678:682'>臧兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='682:705'>　肩牡狼皆稱兩者彼亦有之此亦有之也故上皆稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='705:715'>　並驅下皆言從兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='715:741'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-3a' );" name="005-3a" class="pb">[005-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='741:764'>　　聞音曰還旬緣切間居賢切茂莫口切道徒厚切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='764:773'>　　　好許厚切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='773:803'>　　聞跡曰峱山在齊地當是如犬形嶑山<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR4074' title='KR4074' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR4074.png'/>山皆取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='803:810'>　　　形似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='810:830'>　　聞人曰以子為稱以揖為禮似是士大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='830:853'>　　聞事曰竝驅不必同行東西相遇亦曰並並言旁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='853:866'>　　　也漢書並音補曠切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='866:889'>總聞曰此中土常態亦不必太誇當是輕儇驕恣之人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='889:915'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-3b' );" name="005-3b" class="pb">[005-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='915:938'>非嘉士也不若大叔于田將叔無狃戒其傷女此頗有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='938:947'>愛主及物之情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='947:952'>　　著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='952:959'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='959:967'>俟我於著乎而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='967:982'>　君子與婦人成昏相肅之際也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='982:997'>充耳以素乎而尚之以瓊華乎而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='997:1004'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1004:1030'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-4a' );" name="005-4a" class="pb">[005-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1030:1051'>俟我於庭乎而充耳以青乎而尚之以瓊瑩乎而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1051:1058'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1058:1079'>俟我於堂乎而充耳以黄乎而尚之以瓊英乎而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1079:1102'>　言其服不言其人似鄙其人也或指服為美或指服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1102:1125'>　為惡尚餙也言餙即不足于真美加餙以外美故知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1125:1132'>　為鄙辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1132:1155'>　　聞音曰著直居切素孫租切華芳無切瑩于平切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1155:1164'>　　　英於良切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1164:1190'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-4b' );" name="005-4b" class="pb">[005-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1190:1213'>總聞曰當是貴勢耑事服餙稍虧禮文故女子有望辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1213:1236'>三進而三見易服乎疑辭而鄙辭此女子必有識者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1236:1255'>今東人下流相語皆以而殺聲玩易之意也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1255:1263'>　　東方之日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1263:1270'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1270:1277'>東方之日兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1277:1300'>　東方日出謂寅卯間也東方月出謂十五六間也此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1300:1313'>　男女竊合同邁之日時也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1313:1339'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-5a' );" name="005-5a" class="pb">[005-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1339:1357'>彼姝者子在我室兮在我室兮履我即兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1357:1364'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1364:1387'>東方之月兮彼姝者子在我闥兮在我闥兮履我發兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1387:1410'>　此男子本誘婦人而来乃若無故而至者佯為驚狀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1410:1433'>　欲攜婦人而去乃若見廹不得已者佯為窘狀此滛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1433:1456'>　夫而又有狡數者也即就也發起也履踐也凡足所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1456:1476'>　就所起之地皆履踐之俗謂一歩踏一歩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1476:1489'>總聞曰婦人墮其詭計可憐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1489:1515'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-5b' );" name="005-5b" class="pb">[005-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1515:1523'>　　東方未眀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1523:1530'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1530:1548'>東方未眀顛倒衣裳顛之倒之自公召之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1548:1555'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1555:1573'>東方未晞顛倒裳衣倒之顛之自公令之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1573:1580'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1580:1598'>折柳樊圃狂夫瞿瞿不能辰夜不夙則莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1598:1621'>　赴朝不厭早興趙盾所以却鉏麑也况欲曉未曉當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1621:1647'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-6a' );" name="005-6a" class="pb">[005-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1647:1670'>　興乆矣此必是醉亂之中偶有徴召之命而以非時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1670:1693'>　召臣咎其君以逞狂駭人罪其使至以我折柳為藩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1693:1716'>　故狂夫得越也俗所謂放鵰者也既挟持其君又挟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1716:1739'>　持其將命之人言以君召臣非早則晚不過在日未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1739:1762'>　有在夜者也君召有急則非時至之安論早夜此臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1762:1773'>　當是狡膓凶德者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1773:1796'>　　聞音曰眀謨郎切顛之因切令離呈切圃博故切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1796:1813'>　　　瞿俱具切夜羊茹切莫幕故切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1813:1839'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-6b' );" name="005-6b" class="pb">[005-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='1839:1862'>總聞曰君不能御下臣不能奉上君命不俟駕而行何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='1862:1885'>咎之有雖其君有以致之然其臣亦太難堪也舊説歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='1885:1903'>過於君恐未然又歸過於壼人似亦無謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='1903:1909'>　　南山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='1909:1916'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='1916:1926'>南山崔崔雄狐綏綏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='1926:1949'>　雄者如此雌者可知當是士大夫之在田野者作此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='1949:1972'>　故以南山野狐起辭其中麻畆薪斧皆田野之物此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='1972:1998'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-7a' );" name="005-7a" class="pb">[005-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='1998:2018'>　必士大夫所居在南山而近魯道所見者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2018:2036'>魯道有蕩齊子由歸既曰歸止曷又懐止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2036:2059'>　毛氏襄公文姜之醜見魯桓十八年既歸於人雖故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2059:2071'>　情亦宜斷何尚有懐也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2071:2078'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2078:2101'>葛屨五兩冠緌雙止魯道有蕩齊子庸止既曰庸止曷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2101:2106'>又從止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2106:2129'>　葛屨在足冠緌在首各有所麗不可差也文姜雖齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2129:2155'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-7b' );" name="005-7b" class="pb">[005-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2155:2178'>　妹而魯婦既用此禮其勢豈可以復相從責齊表之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2178:2182'>　辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2182:2189'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2189:2212'>蓺麻如之何衡從其畆取妻如之何必告父母既曰告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2212:2219'>止曷又鞠止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2219:2242'>　麻必附畆而蓺妻必告父母而取言文姜初以告父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2242:2265'>　母為夫婦正也婚而不能以正裁制飬成至此自是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2265:2275'>　而下責魯桓之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2275:2301'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-8a' );" name="005-8a" class="pb">[005-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2301:2308'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2308:2331'>析薪如之何匪斧不克取妻如之何匪媒不得既曰得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2331:2338'>止曷又極止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2338:2361'>　薪必以斧而析妻必以媒而成言文姜初以媒妁而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2361:2384'>　為夫婦亦正也大率其初皆以正而其末乃流于惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2384:2391'>　至此極也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2391:2414'>　　聞音曰懐胡隈切雙所終切畆莫後切母莫後切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2414:2423'>　　　告姑沃切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2423:2449'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-8b' );" name="005-8b" class="pb">[005-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2449:2472'>總聞曰文姜鄭忽所辭者也以為賢而不娶識者更詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2472:2478'>　　甫田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2478:2485'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2485:2495'>無田甫田維莠驕驕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2495:2518'>　田大則人功難周故多莠人逺則國力難及故多勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2518:2522'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2522:2532'>無思逺人勞心忉忉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2532:2555'>　此人似是襄公古人取名不一且以童年取名言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2555:2581'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-9a' );" name="005-9a" class="pb">[005-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2581:2604'>　襄公諸兒即其身取晋侯小子潞子嬰兒亦即其身</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2604:2623'>　取此詩稱總角至突弁略似襄公氣象也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2623:2630'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2630:2648'>無田甫田維莠桀桀無思逺人勞心怛怛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2648:2655'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2655:2673'>婉兮孌兮總角丱兮未幾見兮突而弁兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2673:2692'>　初見童稚忽見長成言年長而識不長也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2692:2703'>　　聞音曰丱扃縣切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2703:2729'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-9b' );" name="005-9b" class="pb">[005-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='2729:2752'>總聞曰此老臣事㓜君之辭不曉者以為孩撫其君曉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='2752:2775'>者以為真愛其君也襄公自掩紀之後必啓其圖逺之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='2775:2798'>心而有無厭之志此臣當已先覺連稱管至父之釁有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='2798:2818'>萌不若姑置逺而且防近也似是鮑叔牙之流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='2818:2824'>　　盧令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='2824:2831'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='2831:2841'>盧令令其人美且仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='2841:2864'>　言縱犬獵獸之人也此事仁者為之方為美也下章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='2864:2891'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-10a' );" name="005-10a" class="pb">[005-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='2891:2900'>　他美皆生於此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='2900:2907'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='2907:2917'>盧重環其人美且鬈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='2917:2924'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='2924:2934'>盧重鋂其人美且偲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='2934:2957'>　　聞音曰令盧經切説文獜□也引詩盧獜獜可從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='2957:2980'>　　　若從本文作鈴聲亦可環胡涓切偲新齎切説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='2980:2990'>　　　文以思得聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='2990:3017'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-10b' );" name="005-10b" class="pb">[005-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3017:3040'>總聞曰此當是旁觀而為之夸譽者也能以仁為首辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3040:3052'>則作此詩者必有識者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3052:3058'>　　敝笱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3058:3065'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3065:3083'>敝笱在梁其魚魴鰥齊子歸止其從如雲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3083:3106'>　敝笱在梁則魚之恣適可知齊姜之狀如此當有同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3106:3125'>　惡相為慫慂者衆也故曰如雲如雨如水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3125:3132'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3132:3159'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-11a' );" name="005-11a" class="pb">[005-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3159:3177'>敝笱在梁其魚魴鱮齊子歸止其從如雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3177:3184'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3184:3202'>敝笱在梁其魚唯唯齊子歸止其從如水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3202:3221'>　　聞音曰鰥姑倫切鱮才呂切唯維癸切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3221:3244'>　　聞訓曰惟毛氏以為出入不制鄭氏以為行相隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3244:3260'>　　　順猶人譍諾曰唯隨順者是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3260:3283'>總聞曰南山歸魯之時此則如齊之時也蓋魯桓未殞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3283:3306'>雖未殞如無人如笱既敝而在梁烏能制魚也其他㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3306:3333'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-11b' );" name="005-11b" class="pb">[005-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3333:3346'>齊則魯桓已殞雖笱亦無也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3346:3352'>　　載驅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3352:3359'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3359:3377'>載驅薄薄簟茀朱鞹魯道有蕩齊子發夕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3377:3387'>　以暮發言心急也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3387:3394'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3394:3412'>四驪濟濟垂轡濔濔魯道有蕩齊子豈弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3412:3419'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3419:3446'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-12a' );" name="005-12a" class="pb">[005-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3446:3464'>汶水湯湯行人彭彭魯道有蕩齊子翶翔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3464:3471'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3471:3489'>汶水滔滔行人儦儦魯道有蕩齊子逰遨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3489:3512'>　　聞音曰薄普各切夕祥龠切弟待禮切湯失章切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3512:3521'>　　　彭必旁切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='3521:3544'>　　聞訓曰豈弟樂易也在詩皆為美稱故鄭氏疑之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='3544:3567'>　　　以豈為闓以弟為圛言開眀猶發夕也以為古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='3567:3590'>　　　文尚書以弟為圛今攷皆無樂易猶彷徉與下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='3590:3617'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-12b' );" name="005-12b" class="pb">[005-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='3617:3628'>　　　文相應不强改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='3628:3651'>　　聞事曰簟茀朱鞹自是文姜所乗之餙不必言襄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='3651:3674'>　　　公盖謂朱鞹諸侯之路車故以為齊侯是時文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='3674:3697'>　　　姜若乗魯侯之車何人能禁文勢自是文姜也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='3697:3720'>總聞曰文姜自歸魯之後一與莊公如齊出魯還魯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='3720:3743'>後五自㑹齊杜氏夫人為魯人所責故出奔内諱奔故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='3743:3766'>謂之孫又文姜與桓俱行而桓為齊所殺故不敢還若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='3766:3789'>爾則非奔也又文姜未還故傳稱文姜出姜于是感公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='3789:3816'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-13a' );" name="005-13a" class="pb">[005-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='3816:3836'>意而還若爾則復還也此詩當在孫齊之後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='3836:3842'>　　猗嗟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='3842:3849'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='3849:3872'>猗嗟昌兮頎而長兮抑若揚兮美目揚兮巧趨蹌兮射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='3872:3877'>則臧兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='3877:3884'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='3884:3907'>猗嗟名兮美目清兮儀既成兮終日射侯不出正兮展</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='3907:3912'>我甥兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='3912:3939'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-13b' );" name="005-13b" class="pb">[005-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='3939:3962'>　俗傳外甥多似舅或魯莊稍肖齊襄好騰口者遂有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='3962:3985'>　齊侯之子之稱故詩人為魯莊解謗言信為我甥也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='3985:3992'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='3992:4015'>猗嗟孌兮清揚婉兮舞則選兮射則貫兮四矢反兮以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4015:4020'>禦亂兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4020:4043'>　齊莊與文姜㑹禚㑹榖猶在齊地至防則不㑹齊地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4043:4066'>　而㑹魯地恐越境貽患故齊人諷魯莊防變言不若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4066:4083'>　反去矢而禦内亂盖懲魯桓之事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4083:4110'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-14a' );" name="005-14a" class="pb">[005-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4110:4133'>　　聞音曰正諸盈切貫扃縣切反孚絇切亂盧眷切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4133:4156'>　　聞訓曰昌名孌皆譽其才之辭長清婉皆譽其貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4156:4179'>　　　之辭不應二章目上為名目下為清不必從爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4179:4195'>　　　雅止作名譽之名文勢為佳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4195:4218'>總聞曰桓公父也文姜母也莊公子也莊公早年而桓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4218:4241'>公已殁文姜已出其後縱横徃来魯齊之間挾母之尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4241:4264'>倚齊之強安可防閑雖髙世大賢處此亦難以為魯莊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4264:4287'>無出羣之英斷無化物之妙用則可失子道則太過也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4287:4314'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-14b' );" name="005-14b" class="pb">[005-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4314:4338'>自舜之後豈可輕以此責人莊公未見可罪但見可憐爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4338:4343'>　魏風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4343:4349'>　　葛屨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4349:4356'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4356:4374'>糾糾葛屨可以履霜摻摻女手可以縫裳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4374:4397'>　葛屨忽已履霜言時易遷夏忽冬也女手忽已縫裳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4397:4420'>　言人易長小忽大也當嫁之時也下所謂佩其象揥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4420:4425'>　亦同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4425:4452'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-15a' );" name="005-15a" class="pb">[005-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4452:4459'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4459:4477'>要之襋之好人服之好人提提宛然左辟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4477:4500'>　要䙅襋領也好人服之者言將適人以此供夫服也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4500:4523'>　好人提提夫壻行將至也提提渉泥水貌宛然左辟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4523:4546'>　忽已在左也旁邊貌妻父母之前男居左女居右今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4546:4570'>　猶言左辟右辟辟有數訓一辟有積言稠叠也一摘辟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4570:4593'>　言多禮節也一糾摘也一眩也一邪也一法也一君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='4593:4616'>　也一除也此當為除言礙路過兩旁故曰除道此皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='4616:4643'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-15b' );" name="005-15b" class="pb">[005-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='4643:4666'>　入聲去聲囘也毛氏不敢當尊宛然而左辟亦在旁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='4666:4680'>　之意陸氏讀作避叶揥恐非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='4680:4687'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='4687:4701'>佩其象揥維是褊心是以為刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='4701:4724'>　言婚嫁太速其意欲早使夫力婦功以濟其家不虚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='4724:4747'>　度也此所以為褊而可刺也今河東風俗如此人家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='4747:4770'>　無有聞食者雖幼兒稚女亦隨力有職易林引此絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='4770:4793'>　紵布帛人所衣服摻摻女手絃績繕織南國饒足取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='4793:4820'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-16a' );" name="005-16a" class="pb">[005-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='4820:4843'>　之有息自北言之則魏近南故曰南國此其民風大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='4843:4848'>　略也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='4848:4871'>　　聞音曰服滿北切辟吴氏毗義切叶揥刺今連上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='4871:4897'>　　　叶襋服刺七賜切當與<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span>相近如雌為妻此為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='4897:4911'>　　　泚今俗讀吪吴氏良是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='4911:4925'>　　聞章曰舊二章今為三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='4925:4948'>總聞曰既以民待之安有葛屨不可履霜今民草履不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='4948:4971'>問嚴寒烈雪細民皆然又安得廟見三月方可執婦功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='4971:4998'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-16b' );" name="005-16b" class="pb">[005-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='4998:5021'>又安得為女不可縫下服女子亦有下服如衵服皆與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5021:5044'>男子同制此亦非所以待民也毛氏鄭氏之説識者更</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5044:5047'>詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5047:5054'>　　汾沮洳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5054:5061'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5061:5084'>彼汾沮洳言采其莫彼其之子美無度美無度殊異乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5084:5088'>公路</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5088:5111'>　水際采草為人葅采木為蠶飼此窮賤之事也賦丰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5111:5138'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-17a' );" name="005-17a" class="pb">[005-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5138:5159'>　美之容而躬窮賤之役殊不似貴族訝之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5159:5166'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5166:5189'>彼汾一方言采其桑彼其之子美如英美如英殊異乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5189:5193'>公行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5193:5200'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5200:5223'>彼汾一曲言采其藚彼其之子美如玉美如玉殊異乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5223:5227'>公族</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5227:5246'>　　聞音曰莫末故切英於良切行戶郎切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5246:5273'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-17b' );" name="005-17b" class="pb">[005-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5273:5296'>　　聞物曰莫茂子也如楮實藚澤㵼也牛脣初生皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5296:5308'>　　　可葅亦謂牛脣菜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5308:5331'>　　聞跡曰班氏魏在晋南河曲故曰彼汾一曲寘諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5331:5354'>　　　河之側不必如此水豈有無曲莫不有側特語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5354:5363'>　　　法若此爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5363:5386'>總聞曰貴者肯任賤者之事為人所難當為衆所服而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5386:5409'>見者已有殊異之辭寖生輕心當是障固山澤奪凡民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5409:5414'>所資也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5414:5441'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-18a' );" name="005-18a" class="pb">[005-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5441:5448'>　　園有桃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5448:5455'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5455:5478'>園有桃其實之殽心之憂矣我歌且謡不知我者謂我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5478:5501'>士也驕彼人是哉子曰何其心之憂矣其誰知之其誰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5501:5509'>知之盖亦勿思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5509:5516'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5516:5539'>園有棘其實之食心之憂矣聊以行國不知我者謂我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5539:5562'>士也㒺極彼人是哉子曰何其心之憂矣其誰知之其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5562:5589'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-18b' );" name="005-18b" class="pb">[005-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5589:5598'>誰知之蓋亦勿思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='5598:5621'>　采桃實以為殽采棘實以為食士大夫朋友相與㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='5621:5644'>　集游適者也但其憂不知何事發之歌謡付之行國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='5644:5667'>　必有難言而不可顯陳者也當時寡識者以歌謡為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='5667:5690'>　縱情而事驕佚以行國為騁意而無終窮懐憂者稍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='5690:5714'>　辨數之彼人君也是此事也言不君也何其當如何也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='5714:5737'>　言將亡也我之所憂人所不知所以不知者特不思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='5737:5760'>　而已苟思則與我同憂也此必其君或愎而自是或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='5760:5787'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-19a' );" name="005-19a" class="pb">[005-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='5787:5810'>　昏而無知而君子避患隠憂為國而有此風大不美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='5810:5814'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='5814:5833'>　　聞音曰哉將黎切思新齎切國越逼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='5833:5856'>　　聞人曰魏自周惠王庚申為晉所滅以封畢萬當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='5856:5879'>　　　時已有先覺者卜偃以為魏大名也萬盈數也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='5879:5902'>　　　畢萬之後必大司馬氏以為自晋獻公卒四子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='5902:5925'>　　　争立而畢萬之後彌大自晉文公入而武子有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='5925:5948'>　　　功晋悼公立而昭子又有功獻子桓子奕世愈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='5948:5975'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-19b' );" name="005-19b" class="pb">[005-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='5975:5998'>　　　張此當是有識者憂晋之終為魏有也但不知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='5998:6021'>　　　在何時周威烈王戊寅始建國裂晋分邦與韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='6021:6044'>　　　趙同恢形勢已乆卜偃能見于初封之時而况</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='6044:6067'>　　　寖乆而寖現乎此士大夫與朋友相與言者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='6067:6090'>　　　故曰子曰何其此人未必深相知然可與言者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6090:6096'>　　　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6096:6119'>總聞曰鄭氏魏君薄公税省國用不取於民食園桃而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6119:6142'>已不修徳教民無以戰此侵削之由惟患公税不薄國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6142:6169'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-20a' );" name="005-20a" class="pb">[005-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6169:6192'>用不省雖食園桃何害土階茅茨此堯所為聖人也德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6192:6215'>教孰大於此有君如是凡民願戴何患無以戰此富强</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='6215:6229'>之本非侵削之端也識者更詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='6229:6235'>　　陟岵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='6235:6242'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='6242:6268'>陟彼岵兮瞻望父兮父曰嗟<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予子行役夙夜無已上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='6268:6277'>慎旃哉猶来無止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='6277:6300'>　此已解而尚相顧子有恨無言瞻望而已其父之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='6300:6327'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-20b' );" name="005-20b" class="pb">[005-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='6327:6351'>　督以勤勉以謹如此尚可来歸母兄之辭皆然止留也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='6351:6374'>　病而留所在不能歸也弃遺也鈍而不及其部伍不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='6374:6397'>　能同歸也死甚于止弃也皆庶幾不如此悲之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='6397:6404'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='6404:6430'>陟彼屺兮瞻望母兮母曰嗟<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予季行役夙夜無寐上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='6430:6439'>慎旃哉猶来無棄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='6439:6446'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='6446:6472'>陟彼岡兮瞻望兄兮兄曰嗟<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予弟行役夙夜必偕上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='6472:6499'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-21a' );" name="005-21a" class="pb">[005-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='6499:6508'>慎旃哉猶來無死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='6508:6524'>　與部伍偕行不可獨後後必刑也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='6524:6547'>　　聞音曰岵後五切父扶雨切子奨禮切屺坡里切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='6547:6570'>　　　母滿罪切兄虚王切弟待禮切偕舉里切死想</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='6570:6577'>　　　止切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='6577:6595'>　　聞句曰嗟斷句文勢當然語意愈切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='6595:6618'>總聞曰毛氏父尚義母尚恩兄尚親尋詩予子予季予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='6618:6641'>弟之辭皆親也夙夜上愼之辭皆義也無止無棄無死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='6641:6668'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-21b' );" name="005-21b" class="pb">[005-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='6668:6691'>之辭皆恩也偶行役者少子爾非專愛其少子也若使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6691:6701'>孟子仲子當亦復然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6701:6709'>　　十畆之間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6709:6716'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='6716:6733'>十畆之間兮桑者閑閑兮行與子還兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='6733:6756'>　居民唯恐其不多上固欲如此下亦欲如此翕集則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='6756:6779'>　舒愉此樂國之象也當是人多桑少為權力所障固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='6779:6802'>　采摘故民他求桑以育蠶爾今鄉落之間蠶時至為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='6802:6829'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-22a' );" name="005-22a" class="pb">[005-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='6829:6852'>　急廹近無所取則逺無所不至有有獲而徑歸者有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='6852:6875'>　無獲而不肯空歸前邁而逺求者此或還或逝者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='6875:6882'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='6882:6899'>十畆之外兮桑者泄泄兮行與子逝兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='6899:6918'>　　聞音曰間居賢切閑胡田切泄以世切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='6918:6941'>總聞曰魏俗多以蠶為業以縑轉食蓋地勢隘而稼事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='6941:6964'>不廣也蠶月壯者用力於外弱者用力於内晝夜奔疲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='6964:6987'>今其風尚如此閑空也言桑葉稀也泄漏也言桑䕃薄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='6987:7014'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-22b' );" name="005-22b" class="pb">[005-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='7014:7037'>也受畆之内無所取受畆之外又無所取以他求也亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='7037:7047'>可見當時促廹氣象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='7047:7053'>　　伐檀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='7053:7060'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='7060:7083'>坎坎伐檀兮寘之河之干兮河水清且漣猗不稼不穡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='7083:7106'>胡取禾三百㕓兮不狩不獵胡曕爾庭有懸貆兮彼君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='7106:7114'>子兮不素餐兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='7114:7137'>　君子伐檀以易食非無故而取給者也不稼穡者胡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='7137:7164'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-23a' );" name="005-23a" class="pb">[005-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='7164:7187'>　為而取禾不狩獵者胡為而懸貆胡言汝何為而乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='7187:7210'>　如此也君子不然計木之大小長短為資之贏虧多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='7210:7223'>　寡非拱手端坐而圖飽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='7223:7230'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='7230:7253'>坎坎伐輻兮寘之河之側兮河水清且直猗不稼不穡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='7253:7276'>胡取禾三百億兮不狩不獵胡瞻爾庭有懸特兮彼君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='7276:7284'>子兮不素食兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='7284:7291'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='7291:7318'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-23b' );" name="005-23b" class="pb">[005-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='7318:7341'>坎坎伐輪兮寘之河之漘兮河水清且淪猗不稼不穡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='7341:7364'>胡取禾三百囷兮不狩不獵胡瞻爾庭有懸鶉兮彼君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='7364:7372'>子兮不素飱兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='7372:7395'>　後章言輻言輪則前章所以伐檀者蓋為此具也毛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='7395:7405'>　氏檀輻檀輪良是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='7405:7428'>　　聞音曰檀徒沿切干居焉切餐七宣切側莊力切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='7428:7437'>　　　飱須倫切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='7437:7460'>總聞曰覩河之清感君子之潔當是在清河清漳附近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='7460:7487'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-24a' );" name="005-24a" class="pb">[005-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='7487:7510'>大率詩人觸境而後興辭河本渾而以為清或者即委</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='7510:7521'>曲解釋此談詩之獘也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='7521:7527'>　　碩鼠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='7527:7534'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='7534:7557'>碩鼠碩鼠無食我黍三嵗貫女莫我肯顧逝將去女適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='7557:7570'>彼樂土樂土樂土爰得我所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='7570:7593'>　此必為吏臨民者習熟至於三年爾不相顧我亦不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='7593:7616'>　想戀凡人情一年猶有望二年已生心三年遂决志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='7616:7643'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-24b' );" name="005-24b" class="pb">[005-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='7643:7666'>　不皆如此大略如此也謂鼠無食我黍無食我麥無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='7666:7678'>　食我苗遺我為行資也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='7678:7685'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='7685:7708'>碩鼠碩鼠無食我麥三嵗貫女莫我肯徳逝将去女適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='7708:7721'>彼樂國樂國樂國爰得我直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='7721:7744'>　直價也所攜之黍之麥之苗苗萊也毛氏苗嘉糓也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='7744:7767'>　茅方苗則可茹榖方苗未可飯也言以此物于他國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='7767:7790'>　轉易以為生不虧其價也今人稱當價猶曰直杜氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='7790:7817'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-25a' );" name="005-25a" class="pb">[005-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='7817:7840'>　城中斗米換衾裯相許寧論兩相直此言至急不復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='7840:7846'>　論直也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='7846:7853'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='7853:7876'>碩鼠碩鼠無食我苗三嵗貫女莫我肯勞逝將去女適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='7876:7889'>彼樂郊樂郊樂郊誰之永號</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l445' data-llen='7889:7912'>　永號言不知在後而不能前者何人長號也以去為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l446' data-llen='7912:7920'>　喜以留為憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l447' data-llen='7920:7939'>　　聞音曰顧果五切麥訖力切國越逼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l448' data-llen='7939:7966'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '005-25b' );" name="005-25b" class="pb">[005-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l449' data-llen='7966:7989'>　　聞字曰勞即下泉郇伯勞之之勞彼去音此平音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l450' data-llen='7989:8009'>　　　音不同意則一吕氏春秋注作逃無謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l451' data-llen='8009:8032'>　　聞訓曰永號難為歌號先號咷而後笑喜悲自是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l452' data-llen='8032:8051'>　　　兩事歌號自是兩音語勢亦不如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l453' data-llen='8051:8074'>總聞曰以鼠斥君度民心雖甚怨之亦不至此又以三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l454' data-llen='8074:8097'>年大比民于是徙若不堪而他適何俟大比也當是居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l455' data-llen='8097:8120'>官滿三嵗如今三年為任之類三載考績自舜法如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l456' data-llen='8120:8127'>想周制猶然</span><br/>
